 are the ones giving vent and protecting twitter more than twitter itself under the guise of freedom of expression. “I believe that Nigeria still rank among the countries with the freest media in the world today. “Facebook, Google hang out, Whatsapp, Instagram are still operating in Nigeria. “Why will the heavens fall because we are suspending twitter because it is promoting insurgency,’’ he said. The minister reiterated that there was nowhere in the world where activities of twitter was proven to be supporting separatist that it would not be suspended. (NAN)